Robin Stille https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robin_Stille 0 Robin Rochelle Stille (November 24, 1961 – February 9, 1996) was an American actress known for her role in the 1982 slasher film The Slumber Party Massacre as Valerie "Val" Bates. She was sometimes credited as Robin Rochelle.
